name: OCM5-14 STANAG small magazine
description: A compact 14-round 5.56 NATO magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, an alternative to the older Ruger .223 mag, it is almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal.

name: OCM5-24 STANAG casket magazine
description: A lightweight 24-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly compact but less reliable and tricky to reload.

name: OCM5-30 STANAG magazine
description: A lighter and more reliable STANAG standard capacity magazine proposed as a replacement for its predecessor of same shape and size, it is almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal.

name: OCM5-50 STANAG drum magazine
description: A lighter and more reliable 50-round STANAG drum magazine proposed as replacement for its predecessor of same shape and size, it is almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal.

name: OCM5-60 STANAG casket magazine
description: A lightweight 60-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly compact but less reliable and tricky to reload.

name: OCM5-100 STANAG casket magazine
description: A lightweight 100-round 5.56 NATO casket magazine compatible with STANAG rifles, almost identical to its version for 5.56 Electrothermal. Amazingly compact but less reliable and tricky to reload.
